}=-3+\\frac{1}{1-x}$ ，\n根据反比例函数 $y=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":526}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"3nne2h","at":1771470893005}},"smart_blocks:20-Product/01-数学教学/试卷/10-试卷汇总/试卷 md 版本/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04694555,0.01267475,0.04167878,-0.08693639,0.00255625,0.02047049,-0.00883045,0.00598218,0.00752374,-0.00847627,0.02829431,-0.05744938,0.04480387,0.00610973,0.01065083,0.00525999,0.03892361,-0.03118656,-0.0662223,-0.01414357,0.13485725,-0.04079549,-0.00805283,-0.04277797,0.06325477,0.03393386,0.02433915,-0.02135521,0.0080879,-0.18736196,0.00080665,0.01286126,-0.00945382,0.0296609,0.03292432,-0.0501302,-0.02085889,0.04579285,-0.0651574,0.01265817,-0.00884507,0.08379341,0.04247797,-0.03624648,0.03470922,-0.02867163,-0.04944289,-0.04206875,0.03750268,-0.00645863,-0.06113387,-0.0010578,-0.00656936,0.02303009,-0.01259527,0.00140734,-0.01695288,0.06111258,0.00931725,-0.00114807,0.04798711,0.00658633,-0.2154202,0.01774878,0.05744365,-0.01473171,-0.01092025,-0.02613604,0.05962016,0.10514129,-0.02915827,-0.00107677,-0.00818477,0.0319693,0.00340369,0.02017782,0.02684615,-0.02534607,-0.04746486,-0.04295783,-0.01179112,0.06894507,0.03552129,0.00434337,0.00363004,0.02421908,0.00649387,-0.05405918,0.01024025,-0.06383011,-0.01940716,-0.0170772,0.00279264,0.02786884,-0.04114721,0.00393263,0.02514907,0.0366127,-0.02377549,0.11053807,-0.04129716,0.08552784,0.00750499,-0.09378482,-0.00488211,-0.05799523,-0.03427375,-0.05972287,-0.02577121,-0.01637504,-0.00122628,-0.03954187,0.05539812,-0.07924808,-0.00763507,-0.01815741,0.05612792,0.02398108,-0.00904356,-0.01126955,0.03506427,0.06226292,0.04161279,-0.05792414,-0.03683339,-0.06710399,0.04230102,0.003203